1.5.0.name: wordpress/interplayplugin
1.5.0.description: The Interplay plugin provides region/leader specific Interplay information directly on you wordpress Website. While use of the plugin and its code are free and open source access to the interplay.org data comes at a fee. Visit http://interplay.org/wordpress to purchase a web service key which will provide your website with data.
